1. create the document library "Spec and Revision Library"
2. Add Multiple People field "Approvers"
3. create the sharepoint list "Workflow Task Item List"
4. Add the following columns to this list:
    Revision Name (text field)
    RevisionId (number field)
    Task Status (choice field) Approve|Reject 
    Comments (free text)

5. create the sharepoint list "Workflow Item List"
6. Add the following columns to this list:
    Revision Name (text field)
    RevisionId (number field)
    Workflow Status (choice field) Initiation|Revision|Accepted|Accepted with Restrictions|Escalate|Rejected


